        "title": "如何评价这波颇具胡佛遗风的操作？",
        "body": "补缴十七年社保，国家预计社保改革后一年多收两万亿，那就意味着这波补缴是十亿级的紧缩政策，贸易战关税也就两千亿刀，这是否意味着新一波大萧条会在中国爆发？\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"aw-upload-img-list\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"/uploads/questions/20180920/ae8a8b19c6ef9210f48d3838eb8139d2.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" data-fancybox-group=\"thumb\" rel=\"lightbox\"><img src=\"/uploads/questions/20180920/ae8a8b19c6ef9210f48d3838eb8139d2.jpg\" class=\"img-thumbnail\" alt=\"7477a7fbd9922a91f66c5c47c70b5aad.jpg\"></a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
